data.title: ‘National Benzole Pink’ large format Giclée Wall Art Print - 90cm x 90cm
data.meta_description: ‘National Benzole Pink’ the enduring power of a brand, hand finished print.This large format Giclée wall art print measures an impressive 90cm x 90cm. Printed on high quality Matte Art Paper using the latest light permanence inks. This listing is for hand finished print only, framing available at separate cost.National Benzole was a popular petroleum brand in the United Kingdom from 1919 to the 1960s. In 1957 the National Benzole Co. became wholly owned by Shell-Mex & BP. In the early 1960s National Benzole was re-branded as National and continued trading as a UK retailer of petroleum products until the early 1990s, the brand was ultimately phased out by parent company BP. National Benzole advertising memorabilia is highly prized amongst collectors.£120.00 including delivery to U.K. zone 1 addresses.For postage costs to addresses outside U.K. zone 1 and overseas postage please enquire prior to placing your order thank you.Please note - the paper stock has a matte finish, colour tones will print with a softer less intense finish than they appear on your screen which is backlit and provides a higher degree of contrast.GBR watermark won’t be present on print.The other items in our photographs are not included.
data.text:
U.K. Postage Information

We follow the widely adopted Royal Mail U.K. postal zones.

If the product description states U.K. Zone 1 postage is included in our price this refers to England, Wales & Scotland (excluding Highlands and Islands).

Prior to placing your order please enquire for postage prices for delivery to the following destinations -

- U.K. Zone 2 - Highlands, Islands of Scotland - enquire for price.

- U.K. Zone 3 - Northern Ireland, Isle of Man, Isles of Scilly - enquire for price.

- Channel Islands - enquire for price.

- Overseas Postage - Rest of the world - enquire for price.

Furniture, larger items and multiple item orders.

For larger items like furniture, more delicate items like mirrors, and restricted items not possible to send by conventional postal services etc., our product descriptions outline that our quoted prices do not include delivery and to ignore any reference during checkout that may mention the inclusion of delivery being included.

We are happy to quote for competitive delivery of these product categories using one of our trusted specialist carriers or using our own transport. Unless otherwise agreed delivery will provided on the basis of kerbside delivery using a single driver who will require assistance to offload if the item is large and or heavy.
